      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，FinTech_AuthVault就是本地DNS，FinTech_LedgerService是TLD。权威服务器单独作为一个participant，叫Servidor Autoritativo。另外需要在Cliente上方加一个注释，用www.google.es作为例子。",
      "elements_involved": [
